        "created_at": "2021-02-19T21:04:28.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>It\u2019s funny \u2013 there is a certain type of name you get which signifies a California meritage wine: Insignia, Symmetry, Elevage, Tapestry, etc.</p>\n<p>Grower Champagne is developing its own \u201cyou can kind of tell that\u2019s what it is\u201d line of names.  Eloquence, Confidence, Resonance, Ouverture, Initial, Empreinte, Efflorescence.</p>",
